{"tid":2257570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"驅趕華漁船 美艦將守西太平洋","createTime":"2020-10-25T09:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T10:46:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"507c1c15130042ec762ada730d01453d96f50100","tid":2257570,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/G7NLM5VAH5CSDGFOPULLOKVHWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FG7NLM5VAH5CSDGFOPULLOKVHWE%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72Pc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=55f66f2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FG7NLM5VAH5CSDGFOPULLOKVHWE%2F&h=0f1d3893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/G7NLM5VAH5CSDGFOPULLOKVHWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n驅趕華漁船 美艦將守西太平洋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4w4w9uQAh1tz5KFUcLBj8w0lJ-U=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4ZIPLAI66NF7RC6JPWUSPNX2PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4w4w9uQAh1tz5KFUcLBj8w0lJ-U%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4ZIPLAI66NF7RC6JPWUSPNX2PA.jpg&h=2dda939d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國海岸警衛隊巡邏艦<br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問奧布萊恩上周五宣佈，為打擊非法捕魚和四處騷擾他國海域的中國漁船，美國已決定在西太平洋部署新一代快速反應巡邏艦，以確保航行自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美歐建渠道商討中國問題<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩發表聲明，批評中國非法、未經報告與未經管制的捕魚行動，以及對在印太其他國家專屬經濟區作業船隻的騷擾，威脅美國與太平洋鄰國主權，並危及區域穩定。他說，美國海岸防衞隊將戰略性地在西太平洋設立母港，部署快速反應巡邏艦，執行海上安全任務，當中包括漁業巡防、近海監視，以及與執法能力有限的區域合作夥伴協作，確保航行自由。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國國務卿蓬佩奧與歐盟外交與安全政策高級代表博雷爾（Josep Borrell）周五。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/路透社"},{"pid":"df3883edf8ae7899fd58ee3dadfc2d73c4727228","tid":2257570,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:38:40.000Z","msg":"中国漁政大戰美國海岸防衛隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba24c37473c6e31644acf2d7d5e347312a89fff","tid":2257570,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大西洋⋯好撚遠。"},{"pid":"3557558a8271ba7b88640dfd91b0ced99aff1d4c","tid":2257570,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dba24c37473c6e31644acf2d7d5e347312a89fff","tid":2257570,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大西洋⋯好撚遠。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己睇錯。<br />\n<br />\n西太平洋，變大西洋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ffd52b84dd161bb0a814024e75b5fc939e77c3","tid":2257570,"uid":54125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"支那啲漁船可以去全世界越界偷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近至尖閣諸島，遠至真係大西洋非洲附近<br />\n<br />\n登登仲講緊話叫佢守國際規則<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ffa7c0248ac9b2d23be2ffbccf5e92a576dcf7","tid":2257570,"uid":267658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3557558a8271ba7b88640dfd91b0ced99aff1d4c","tid":2257570,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dba24c37473c6e31644acf2d7d5e347312a89fff","tid":2257570,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大西洋⋯好撚遠。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己睇錯。<br />\n<br />\n西太平洋，變大西洋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T10:04:52.0